    Return the number of characters that can converse without any character
    having any other character in their set.
    """
    # Parse inputs

    characters = set()

    # Initialize hash map of characters and their translations
    char_translation = {}

    # Add characters to set of characters
    for char in others:
        if char in char_translation:
            char_translation[char] += 1
        else:
            char_translation[char] = 1

    # Convert dictionaries to set
    characters = set(char_translation.keys())

    # Check if set of characters is of size 1
    while len(characters) > 1:

        # Initialize set of characters that can leave
        leaving_characters = set()

        # Iterate through every character
        for char in characters:

            # Add to set of characters that can leave if
            # 1. Character knows any other characters
            # 2. Character can translate to any other
            if char_translation[char] > 0:

                # Check if character can translate
                for char_to_translate in characters:
                    if char in char_translation and char_translation[char] > 0:
                        if not (char_to_translate in char_translation and char_translation[char_to_translate] == 0):
                            char_translation[char_to_translate] += 1

                # Add character to set of characters that can leave
                leaving_characters.add(char)

        # Check if leaving characters is of size 1
        while len(leaving_characters) > 1:

            # Remove first character from set of characters to leave
            new_leaving_characters = set()
            for char in leaving_characters:
                new_leaving_characters.add(char)

            # Remove characters from set of characters to leave
            for char in leaving_characters:
                char_translation[char] -= 1
                if char_translation[char] == 0:
                    del char_translation[char]

            # Add characters to set of characters to leave
            leaving_characters = new_leaving_characters

        # Set of characters left is of size 1
        characters = set(leaving_characters)

    # Return the size of the set of characters left
    return len(characters)
